name: Typed
description:
You think you can type fast? You have 60 seconds to test it, but watch out for those cAPs. Challenge your friends to see who is the fastest.

0-15: Weak sauce.
16-25: Ok...I guess.
26-39: You probably text way too much.
40 and over: You're a unicorn, or you wasted a few seconds of your life watching a video (thanks btw).
